'''GPnotebook''' is a [[United Kingdom|British]] medical database for [[general practitioners]] (GPs).<ref>[http://www.leeds.ac.uk/library/subjects/medicine/websites.php Selected sites for medicine] description of site at University of Leeds library.</ref> It is an online [[encyclopaedia]] of [[medicine]] that provides an immediate reference resource for [[clinician]]s worldwide. The database consists of over 30,000 pages of information. 

A RCGP article describing the history of GPnotebook is available https://bjgp.org/content/64/619/92

GPnotebook is provided online by Oxbridge Solutions Limited.

